ICO.Description:
CEDEX is a certified blockchain-based diamong exchange that allows anyone to invest in indidual diamonds, shares of a high-value stone or shares in a basket of diamonds (ETF). The CEDEX Exchange is powered by the CEDEX Coin, an ERC20 token based on the Ethereum network. It allows users to puchase diamonds on CEDEX.

 

Team:

  • Saar Levi: CEO and Co-Founder 
  • Ronen Priewer: Founder 
  • Avner Lewenstein: CTO and Serial Blockchain Developer 
  • Evengi Kif: Head of Product 
  • Aviv Balassiano: Development Manager 

The CEDEX ICO will start on the 16th of March. The ICO token allocation represents 50% of the total token supply and will be available for a 0.8 USD starting price. Users can purchase tokens with BTC and ETH. The ICO funding cap is set at $40,000,000.

Token Reserve Split:

  • 50% Token Sale
  • 15% Bonuses
  • 10% Team and Advisory
  • 15% The Company
  • 5% Founders
  • 5% Outsourced services

The CEDEX ICO features a bonus and bounty campaign.

Bonus Structure:

  • Pre-sale - up to 25%
  • First day of sale - up to 25% (ending at 24:00 GMT)
